title: Match Making Please!
body: Should this be happening at start of season mid Friday night!

replies.body: Actually, based on OP.GG, it does seem reasonably balanced. A couple of the golds on the enemy team have low MMR, matching Gold 3 or lower, and a couple on your team have higher MMR. OP.GG is saying Kial has around 1700 MMR, despite being unranked. It could be a lot worse.
